org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_Foundations.CoreElements

Interface CoreElementsPackage.Literals

  • Enclosing interface:
    CoreElementsPackage

    public static interface CoreElementsPackage.Literals
    Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
    • each class,
    • each feature of each class,
    • each enum,
    • and each data type
